and that it's time to move

20:17.600 --> 20:19.467 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
on.

20:19.467 --> 20:21.567 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Is
Paul Manafort being
investigated in any way now?

20:21.567 --> 20:25.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFF HORWITZ: So, yes, there
