in front of committees in
either the Senate or the House.

20:44.500 --> 20:47.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so that, I think, is going
to be something where we might
be getting a bit more public

20:47.533 --> 20:49.667 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
exposure to this.

20:49.667 --> 20:51.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And, to be
