that he no longer was chairman

20:51.933 --> 20:53.233 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
of Donald Trump's campaign.

20:53.233 --> 20:54.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That is kind of
a separate issue.

20:54.500 --> 20:56.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFF HORWITZ: No, no.

20:56.633 --> 21:00.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He left the campaign in August
amid a whole bunch of concerns
as to whether they -- first

21:02.567 --> 21:06.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
