cash payments in a way that

21:07.633 --> 21:09.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
was potentially illicit.

21:09.033 --> 21:10.967 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That was sort of a
controversy back then.

21:10.967 --> 21:15.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And then we also reported
in, I believe, in 2013, he
actually had been doing lobbying

21:17.700 --> 21:21.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
