in the United States on behalf

21:22.533 --> 21:25.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of those Ukrainian interests
without disclosing it.

21:25.300 --> 21:29.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, those two things together
sort of preceded his departure.

21:29.033 --> 21:32.467 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All
right, Jeff Horwitz of
the Associated Press,
joining us from Washington,

21:32.467 --> 21:34.467 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
thanks so much.

21:34.467 --> 21:39.467 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFF HORWITZ: Thank you.

21:41.400 --> 21:46.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In this morning's
Washington Post, some tough
words for President Trump

21:48.133 --> 21:51.267 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
and his administration
