21:51.267 --> 21:56.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We spoke earlier this evening
with former Obama White House
National Security Adviser

21:56.100 --> 21:58.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Susan Rice, the
author of that piece.

21:58.300 --> 22:01.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It was her first interview
since leaving the White House.

22:01.133 --> 22:06.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I began by asking about
the allegations leveled
today by House Intelligence
Committee Chairman

22:08.133 --> 22:11.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Devin Nunes that Trump
transition officials,
including the president,
may have been swept

22:13.300 --> 22:15.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
up in surveillance of
foreigners at the end of
the Obama administration.

22:15.400 --> 22:17.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SUSAN RICE, Former U.S.
National Security Adviser:
I know nothing about this.

22:17.733 --> 22:22.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I was surprised to see
reports from Chairman
Nunes on that count today.

22:24.133 --> 22:27.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And let's back up and
recall where we have been.

22:27.733 --> 22:32.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The president of the United
States accused his predecessor,
President Obama, of wiretapping

22:33.600 --> 22:35.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Trump Tower during the campaign.

22:35.900 --> 22:39.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Nothing of the sort occurred,
and we have heard that
confirmed by the director of the

22:39.700 --> 22:44.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
