Times has reported that,
in the final days of the
Obama administration,

23:40.267 --> 23:44.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
individuals went out of their
way to spread information
throughout the government about

23:44.100 --> 23:49.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
what they knew about
intelligence that the
Russians had interfered
in the election last

23:51.500 --> 23:56.367 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
year, and that there may
have been a connection with
Trump campaign officials.

23:56.367 --> 24:00.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, that story has now been
out there for several weeks.

24:00.133 --> 24:01.333 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
Could there be a
connection here?

24:01.333 --> 24:02.767 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SUSAN RICE: I'm not
aware of any connection.

24:02.767 --> 24:04.833 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I read The New York Times story.

24:04.833 --> 24:08.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I must say, Judy, as one of
the most senior White House
officials and the most senior

24:08.400 --> 24:12.667 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
responsible for national
security, I found that
report a bit perplexing.

24:12.667 --> 24:17.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I wasn't aware of any
orders given to disseminate
that kind of information.

24:17.067 --> 24:18.533 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

24:18.533 --> 24:21.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SUSAN RICE: So, I have no idea
whether that was the case.

24:21.400 --> 24:26.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the fact is that the
president did request
back in December that the
intelligence community

24:29.533 --> 24:34.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
compile all of the information
that it had on what had
transpired during the campaign

24:36.500 --> 24:39.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
with respect to the Russians
involving themselves in
the presidential campaign.

24:39.300 --> 24:44.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And that report was
provided to the American
people in unclassified
form and to Congress

24:45.500 --> 24:47.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
in classified form
in early January.

24:47.533 --> 24:51.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And was there
a concern, though, inside the
Obama administration, inside the

24:51.533 --> 24:56.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
White House that the new Trump
administration might not follow
up on that intelligence that

24:57.267 --> 24:59.367 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
had been gathered?

24:59.367 --> 25:01.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SUSAN RICE: I don't think that
was the concern, because, to
the extent that there was any

25:01.500 --> 25:05.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
need to follow up, it wouldn't
be done necessarily by the White
House, but by the intelligence

25:05.067 --> 25:08.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
community, and by the Justice
Department, if appropriate.

25:08.300 --> 25:13.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think our interest was, and
the president's direction was,
let us make sure that we have

25:13.067 --> 25:17.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
compiled and put together in
one place all the information
that we have, so that it is

25:17.733 --> 25:21.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
there for the new
administration, it's there
for the American people,
and there for Congress

25:21.833 --> 25:23.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to utilize as they see fit.

25:23.900 --> 25:28.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, let's --
that brings us to the opinion
piece that you wrote that

25:28.167 --> 25:33.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
appeared today in The Washington
Post, Ambassador Rice, in which
you -- what you describe as

25:35.567 --> 25:38.767 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a pattern of false
statements from this
president could jeopardize
the national security of

25:40.233 --> 25:41.367 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
this country.

25:41.367 --> 25:42.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's a serious charge.

25:42.533 --> 25:43.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What did you mean by that?

25:43.733 --> 25:45.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
SUSAN RICE: Well,
let me explain, Judy.

25:45.800 --> 25:49.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think the American people
know that, over the last weeks
of the administration, it's

25:51.533 --> 25:54.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
now been almost -- almost
exactly two months - - we have
heard a number of striking and

25:56.900 --> 26:00.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
actually patently misleading
statements from not only the
president, but also from his

26:02.700 --> 26:04.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
principal spokespersons.

26:04.833 --> 26:09.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And those statements are heard
and digested by the rest of
the world, whether they are

26:09.233 --> 26:11.633 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
our friends or our adversaries.

26:11.633 --> 26:16.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Wall Street Journal
made a very similar point
today on its editorial page.

26:16.333 --> 26:21.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And the point is this: The
United States of America is
the leading power in the world.

26:23.233 --> 26:26.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Our friends and our adversaries
respect us in large measure
because they know that we

26:27.533 --> 26:28.333 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
are steady.

26:28.333 --> 26:29.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We are fact-based.

26:29.233 --> 26:31.267 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
We are serious.

26:31.267 --> 26:35.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And when we have the White House
of the United States putting
out information that everybody

26:38.267 --> 26:41.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
can see to be inaccurate,
if not deliberately false,
it shakes the credibility
and the confidence

26:43.200 --> 26:47.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of our allies, and it lends
doubt to our adversaries
who may miscalculate.

26:47.600 --> 26:51.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it undermines the confidence
of the American people in what
comes out of the White House,

26:51.900 --> 26:56.567 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
which is very detrimental in
the event we have a national
crisis and we need to rally

26:56.567 --> 26:58.633 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
around the flag.

26:58.633 --> 27:02.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But, just to play
devil's advocate for a moment,
how do you or how does anyone

27:02.933 --> 27:07.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
else know, though, that this is
just not the rough beginning,
rocky beginning of a new

27:10.133 --> 27:14.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
administration, and that other
countries can see through
mistakes, whatever you want to

27:14.833 --> 27:19.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
call them, statements,
and they're looking at
the overall picture and
U.S. national security

27:21.267 --> 27:23.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
is not really in jeopardy?

27:23.300 --> 27:27.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SUSAN RICE: Well, Judy, I think
if it were one or two such
statements, and then the -- they

27:29.100 --> 27:32.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
were corrected when the
facts were plain, that
would be one thing.

27:32.633 --> 27:37.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But we have had statements
ranging from the allegation that
three million to five million

27:39.667 --> 27:42.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
illegal immigrants voted in
our elections, which has been
debunked on a bipartisan basis

27:44.767 --> 27:47.567 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
by members of Congress, to
this allegation that we have
already discussed, which was

27:47.567 --> 27:52.567 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
quite shocking, that the
president's predecessor,
President Obama, had
illegally wiretapped

27:54.133 --> 27:57.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
his office building
during the campaign.

27:57.233 --> 28:02.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we have heard from
bipartisan leaders of Congress,
as well as from the director

28:03.800 --> 28:05.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
of the FBI, that there's
no information to
support that allegation.

28:05.900 --> 28:10.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And yet there's been no
correction, no apology.

28:10.033 --> 28:14.367 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think the world is not
impervious to what happens
here in the United States.

28:14.367 --> 28:17.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And, on the contrary, they
watch it very, very carefully.

28:17.433 --> 28:20.667 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And they wonder and worry,
what does this mean?

28:20.667 --> 28:22.667 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Can we trust the word
of the White House?

28:22.667 --> 28:24.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, in the
meantime, different subject.

28:24.800 --> 28:28.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Today, the Trump administration
convened a meet hearing in
Washington of the leaders

28:28.933 --> 28:33.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
from 68 countries to talk
about the fight against
ISIS, the path forward.

28:35.767 --> 28:39.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, among other things,
officials of this administration
are saying the reason ISIS

28:41.700 --> 28:44.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
