is to the world is in part
because of the failed policies

28:45.667 --> 28:47.133 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
of the Obama administration.

28:47.133 --> 28:49.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SUSAN RICE: Well, I think the
facts don't bear that out.

28:49.833 --> 28:54.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The strategy that the Trump
administration is pursuing,
at the behest of the very same

28:56.800 --> 29:00.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
