interpret the Constitution.

31:32.833 --> 31:37.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And she expressed some concern
over what he said before on
the importance of Supreme Court

31:38.500 --> 31:39.500 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
precedent.

31:39.500 --> 31:40.500 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Let's listen.

31:40.500 --> 31:42.167 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

31:42.167 --> 31:44.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
DIANNE FEINSTEIN (D),
California: We talked
about precedent.

31:44.300 --> 31:47.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And what's happened is, every
