gone back and is a no vote.

31:50.633 --> 31:54.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, how does -- how
does one look at you?

31:54.900 --> 31:59.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For the life of me, I really
don't know, when you're there,
what you're going to do with

32:00.433 --> 32:02.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

32:02.533 --> 32:06.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NEIL GORSUCH, Supreme Court
Nominee: Senator, all I can do
is -- I can't promise you how

32:07.467 --> 32:09.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
