nursery to nurture the coral

49:46.767 --> 49:49.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
itself.

49:49.300 --> 49:53.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Most corals are nourished
through a symbiotic
relationship with algae,
that convert sunlight

49:54.800 --> 49:56.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
