comes directly from that
garden in your stomach.

50:05.200 --> 50:09.767 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: The pigments
in the algae are the source
of the vivid rainbow of colors

50:09.767 --> 50:12.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
