50:32.867 --> 50:37.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Jen Smith showed me Birch's
display of an unhealthy
bleached coral reef.

50:37.500 --> 50:41.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JENNIFER SMITH: As long as you
still see white skeleton, that's
usually an indication that

50:41.700 --> 50:46.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
